{"tid":1356373,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯單野真係唔係自編自導？？","createTime":"2019-07-23T13:16:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:35:22.000Z","uid":190239,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"77960d3f86efca71755b26c9d690152fb833d0f0","tid":1356373,"uid":190239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:16:11.000Z","msg":"雖然個個都話想起佢墳 但係拆墳始終都係唔太好 <br />\n我相信唔會係黑衫嘅人做 <br />\n白衫收唔足錢都有可能 但其實只係過左兩日 未收齊錢好正常啫<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以我有理由懷疑件事係何君堯自編自導嘅一場大龍鳳</span></span>"},{"pid":"1a5f11a87893e63852ef8703376ea5b0fc4d305e","tid":1356373,"uid":59700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:16:50.000Z","msg":"係fact checked"},{"pid":"e0ee997791a4403228432e57547dbdba92bb9f75","tid":1356373,"uid":162272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:26:14.000Z","msg":"好彩 幾驚又炒車"},{"pid":"6449c1050ffa4a3d979f4ab330f98b8f38b00e7b","tid":1356373,"uid":250443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:29:16.000Z","msg":"阻阻大家 小弟嘅白宮聯署差兩千咋<br />\n希望request國際人道救援/援助 人道監察<br />\n已經有九萬七千人簽咗 <br />\n係我知 未必work 但呢個簡單嘅步驟 希望咁多位唔好放棄任何一線機會<br />\n希望大家用兩分鐘簽簽佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記住confirm埋email<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens&d=YTg1cObnFWHTBoRPd5eD4RSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=b49587f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/requesting-international-humanitarian-aidassistance-unprotected-hong-kong-citizens</a><br />\n<br />\n大家繼續幫手文宣 各自爬山 山頂見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d34c18b6a6e7dfbedf610055d439d6da8237bcc","tid":1356373,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:35:22.000Z","msg":"太多版本，又話要俾和頭費老新，何妖唔肯孭條數<br />\n又話本身何拍心口話唔會拉，而家又割蓆又開始拉人所以反面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}